                    <span id="c-937808016" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-937808016" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="937808016">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49177836/">布拉格扔出窗外</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-07-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">法兰西的人文主义才是真正的人文主义啊。前半部分还可以 后面德勒兹写的不尽人意</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="970992630">
        <div class="comment">
